  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个Git流程图，展示如何把feature分支合并到main分支。关键是用bottom-to-top的流向，这样更符合我们团队的阅读习惯。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "gitGraph",
        "BT",
        "main",
        "newbranch",
        "merge"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，bottom-to-top就是从下往上生长。那标题我写成\"Merge feature to advanced main (bottom-to-top)\"可以吗？另外需要几个commit节点？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "commit",
        "BT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "标题可以。节点安排上：main分支先有初始commit，然后从main切出newbranch做开发，newbranch上有一个commit，同时main也往前推进了一个commit，最后把newbranch合并回main。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "newbranch",
        "commit",
        "branch",
        "checkout",
        "merge"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我按这个顺序画：先commit，然后branch newbranch，checkout过去再commit，切回main再commit，最后merge newbranch。这样合并点会在main的最新位置。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit",
        "branch newbranch",
        "checkout newbranch",
        "checkout main",
        "merge newbranch"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，merge的方向确认一下——是newbranch合并到main，不是main合并到newbranch对吧？我描述的顺序没问题，但想确保箭头方向正确。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "merge newbranch",
        "main",
        "newbranch"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认，merge newbranch表示把newbranch的内容合并到当前分支，也就是main。箭头会从newbranch指向main的合并点，符合你的需求。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "merge newbranch",
        "main"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "还有一个细节：newbranch上的那个commit，我希望在图里显示它是从main的第二个commit分出来的，这样时间线更清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "newbranch",
        "commit",
        "main",
        "branch"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "没问题，结构已经对齐了：初始commit在底部，然后分支newbranch向上生长，两边各自commit后再汇合。图完成了，你看一下流向和合并点是否符合预期？",
